extendedInfo.description: Moonlight by the sea theme around the idea of a back-lit moon shinning about the backdrop of the sea. A peaceful and tranquil setting to relax when you look at your phone. We spice things up by making it into a 3D cube and added special lighting and particle effects to show what possible on a Live Wallpaper. Features include:Options for transparent box2 different light sourceOption to move lightOption to change viewing angle and change background color.Option for Auto rotation with speed control, or manual control with finger swipe.Contain Ads
